nami'' || \"Yoake no Ane Mosu\" || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kingrecords.co.jp/cs/g/gKICJ-813/|script-title=ja:Canvas \u5357 \u91cc\u6c99|publisher=[[King Records (Japan)|King Records]]|accessdate=April 21, 2020|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" | 2019\n| ''[[Kingdom Hearts]] Orchestra -World of Tres- Album'' || arranged \"Overture to the Decisive Battle\" || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.khinsider.com/forums/index.php?threads/kingdom-hearts-orchestra-world-of-tres-setlist-and-special-messages.219714/|title=Kingdom Hearts Orchestra -World of Tres- Setlist and Special Messages|website=khinsider.com|accessdate=April 21, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190703152736/https://www.khinsider.com/forums/index.php?threads/kingdom-hearts-orchestra-world-of-tres-setlist-and-special-messages.219714/|archive-date=April 21, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Octopath Traveler]] Arrangements Break & Boost -Extend-'' || || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://store.jp.square-enix.com/item/SQEX_10717.html|title=OCTOPATH TRAVELER Arrangements Break & Boost -Extend- |publisher=[[Square Enix]]|accessdate=April 21, 2020|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Azur Lane]]'' || anime || <ref name=\"azur\">{{cite web|url=https://azurlane-anime.jp/staffcast/|title=STAFF&CAST|website=azurlane-anime.jp|accessdate=April 21, 2020|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | 2020\n| ''Granblue Fantasy The Animation 2'' || anime; with Tsutomu Narita || <ref>{{cite web|last=Loo|first=Egan|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-08-03/granblue-fantasy-anime-season-2-1st-promo-reveals-revamped-mappa-staff-cast-october-4-debut/.149672|title=Granblue Fantasy Anime Season 2's 1st Promo Reveals Revamped MAPPA Staff, Cast, October 4 Debut|publisher=[[Anime News Network]]|date=August 3, 2019|accessdate=April 21, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Princess Connect! Re:Dive]]'' || anime; with various others || <ref>{{cite tweet|last=Nishiki|first=Yasunori|user=yasunorinishiki|dat